Amani National Congress party leader, Musalia Mudavadi has warned politicians against forming clusters ahead of the 2022 polls because it could divide the country. Mudavadi also cautioned against the narrative of dynasty and hustler families, saying it is dangerous for the peace and tranquility of this country. He was speaking during the burial of the late mama Elina Anuna the mother to Emuhaya MP Omboko Milemba in Vihiga county. 